data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This enchanting ranch-style residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and charm. With three spacious bedrooms, you'll have plenty of room to unwind and create your own personal oasis.   But wait, there's more! Picture yourself relaxing in the bonus family room, a versatile space that can be transformed into a game room, home theater, or even a yoga retreat. This bonus room is your blank canvas for endless entertainment possibilities.  Step outside onto the covered back porch and be greeted by a tranquil oasis. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue with friends and family, this outdoor space provides the perfect setting for making memories.  With one and a half bathrooms, you'll never have to worry about morning rush hour. Freshen up in style and enjoy the convenience of an additional powder room for guests.
